Description:Verify Attunement activated ability whose cost is "Return Attunement to its owner's hand": draw 3 cards, then discard 4 cards. Regression for the Return<N/Type> activation-cost concept (mtg-913 2000 WC Replenish deck). Before the fix Attunement's whole ability was silently dropped at load time (the cost parser had no Return<...> arm), so it was a do-nothing enchantment.

